<%= javascript_include_tag 'svg-pan-zoom' %>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'maps' %>

<script>
	$(function () {
    $('[data-toggle="popover"]').popover()
  })
</script>

<p>When you select an individual excavation unit, the map will take you to a new page with summary information and panel links to specific units defined for that context.  Once you select a unit, you can browse various categories of available information. </p>

<p>The map tools allow you to toggle between two different versions of Salmon Pueblo: the initial Chaco occupation and the later San Juan occupation.  The Chaco map will provide access only to those units which date to the Chaco era (1090-1125 CE).  The San Juan map will return all units defined for that  context (both Chacoan and post-Chacoan).  </p>

<div class="map_controls">
  <form lpformnum="1">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-3">
        <h3>Map Controls:</h3>
      </div><!-- /col -->
      <div class="col-sm-4 map_trench_controls">
        <strong>Trenches:</strong>
        <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons">
          <label class="btn btn-primary active" onclick="toggle_trenches_on()">
            <input type="radio" name="options" id="toggle_salmon_occ" autocomplete="off" checked > Show
          </label>
          <label class="btn btn-primary" onclick="toggle_trenches_off()">
            <input type="radio" name="options" id="toggle_chaco_occ" autocomplete="off" > Hide
          </label>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /col -->

      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <strong>Occupation:</strong>
        <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons">
          <label class="btn btn-primary active" onclick="toggle_salmon_display()">
            <input type="radio" name="options" id="toggle_salmon_occ" autocomplete="off" checked > San Juan
          </label>
          <label class="btn btn-primary" onclick="toggle_chaco_display()">
            <input type="radio" name="options" id="toggle_chaco_occ" autocomplete="off" > Chaco
          </label>
        </div>

        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign map_occupation_help" aria-hidden="true" data-toggle="popover" data-content="Text for this pop-up: The Chaco-era map will take you to units identified with the Chacaon occupation. The San Juan-era map will show you all units from both occupations."></span>
      </div><!-- /col -->

    </div><!-- /row -->
  </form>
</div><!-- /map_controls -->

</div><!-- /container -->

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div id="map_container">
    <%= render "svg" %>
  </div>
</div>

<%= javascript_include_tag 'map_zoom' %>
